#データの更新
UPDATE テーブル名 SET 変更内容 WHERE 条件;

+------+--------------+-------+
| id   | name         | price |
+------+--------------+-------+
|    1 | ペン         |   120 |
|    2 | 消しゴム     |  NULL |
+------+--------------+-------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)

idが2のレコードを、priceが100となるように更新

UPDATE goods SET price = 100 WHERE id = 2;
SELECT * FROM goods;
+------+--------------+-------+
| id   | name         | price |
+------+--------------+-------+
|    1 | ペン         |   120 |
|    2 | 消しゴム     |   100 |
+------+--------------+-------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)
